resources.string: Sabhi cheezein mita di gayi hain

KUCH ANUDESH

 SCREEN LOCK: video chalate samay, kendriya button ke zariye, screen par anavashyak sparshon ko rokna sambhav hai, battery jeevan ko badhane ke liye chamak ko kam se kam kar diya jata hai.

 PLAYBACK: yah function phone par home button dabane se uplabdh hai, bubble mein vartman mein chal rahi samagri dikhai deti hai. Sangeet niyantran application ko punah kholkar prapt kiya jata hai.

 DELETION: playlist ya geeton ko mitana lambe click se kiya jata hai. Dhyan dein: itihaas video ke liye aapko ise mukhya screen par karna hoga na ki player screen par.

 PLAYLISTS: geet jodna video player ke upar dayein kone mein sthit button ke zariye sambhav hai.
DATA INFO\n\n Kuch data API ke malik, yani ki Youtube dwara, Niyam aur Sharten aur Gopniyata Niti mein diye gaye anusar, her-pher kiya ja sakta hai.
